ew boss! same as the old boss!" and the chorus: "we won't get fooled again!" ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ ------ paul havemann (internet: paul@hsh.com) * they're not just opinions -- they're caffeine for the brain! * ** (up to 50 milligrams per cynical observation.) ** recommended minimum daily requirement: 1,000 mg. keep reading.
